quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  7,74,"Munibuke ubwo yabagiraga abasigire nyuma y’abantu bo mu bwoko bwa Adi, akababeshaho neza ku isi, mukubaka ingoro zanyu mu bibaya, mukanahanga amazu mu misozi. Bityo, nimwibuke inema za Allah (yabahundagajeho) kandi ntimugakwize ubwangizi ku isi"
  7,75,"Ibikomerezwa by’abibone mu bantu be (intumwa Swalehe), byabwiye abemeramana muri byo bari abanyantege nke biti “Ese muzi ko Swalehe yoherejwe na Nyagasani we?” (Abemeramana) baravuga bati “Mu by’ukuri twe twemera ubutumwa yahawe.”"
  7,76,Ba bandi b’abibone baravuga bati “Mu by’ukuri ibyo mwemeye twe turabihakana.”
  7,77,"Nuko ya ngamiya barayica, baba bigometse ku itegeko rya Nyagasani wabo, maze baravuga bati “Yewe Swalehe! Ngaho tuzanire ibyo udukangisha (ibihano) niba koko uri umwe mu ntumwa (za Allah).”"
  7,78,"Ubwo baba batewe n’umutingito, maze bahinduka imirambo bapfukamye mu mazu yabo"
  7,79,"Nuko (Swalehe) arahindukira abatera umugongo, maze aravuga ati “Yemwe bantu banjye! Rwose nabagejejeho ubutumwa bwa Nyagasani wanjye, mbagira n’inama ariko ntimukunda ababagira inama.”"
  7,80,Unibuke (yewe Muhamadi) ubwo Loti yabwiraga abantu be ati “Ese murakora ibikozasoni bitigeze bikorwa na kimwe mu biremwa byabayeho mbere yanyu?”
  7,81,Mu by’ukuri mwe murarikira gukorana imibonano n’abagabo bagenzi banyu musize abagore! Ahubwo muri abantu barengera (amategeko ya Allah)